tspan.tspan: The Turtle is powered by 4 AA batteries.
Install them observing the polarity markings.
Gently rotate the servo arm to the vertical position.
Remove the cap from a marker and install the
collar to the front edge of the "R" in RoseArt.
Place the robot in the center of the paper facing
right (East) and turn the power switch on.
Insert the marker into the barrel until the
collar rests on the servo arm.
